steps.name: Input search text and press Enter
$("app-search form input") set value("Legacy Response Technician (afta8w8)")
Verify that the search result is correct
$("app-search-result ion-card-content app-service-link") should have(text "Legacy Response Technician (afta8w8)")
Verify that the service data is correct
$("app-service-widget") should have(text "Go home and drink, grandpa. It does not do to leave a live dragon out of your calculations, if you live near him.")

parameters.name: serviceDescription
parameters.value: Go home and drink, grandpa. It does not do to leave a live dragon out of your calculations, if you live near him.

steps.name: $("app-service-widget") should have(text "Ordering of this service will be approved automatically")
$("app-book div.calendar/with text: 5") should have([css class "selected", 10 s.])
$("app-time-step main div ion-button") should be([visible, 10 s.])
$("app-time-step div.footer ion-button") should not have([css class "button-disabled", 10 s.])
$("app-time-step div.footer ion-button") should not be([visible, 10 s.])
$("app-confirmation-step div.footer ion-button") should not have([css class "button-disabled", 10 s.])
$("app-confirmation-step div.footer ion-button") should not be([visible, 10 s.])
Click to see sent order details
$("app-sent-order-page app-sent-order div.order-full-info__more-info a") should be([visible, 10 s.])
